messages.message: 3 is a very common ask - I have a canned answer I send over email but most customers want a much more detailed view of what we are doing given they run into correctness issues with logprob when building themselves
@Hamish are the customers having issues with the confidence score being too low or too high? And for which types of fields?

Yeah tbh our user story with confidence scores is incomplete. We have numbers but not true sense of what is good for a field and no way for a user to really determin that. Its a gap I have on my plate to re-review. Saving this as more input
